hopobject.body: We work together dermaglow lip plumper greece An external facet of this is the deep integration of SkyDrive into Windows 8.1 to better marry the Surface 2 (device) and SkyDrive (service). Microsoft is dishing up 200 free gigabytes of SkyDrive capacity to Surface purchasers. Another example is the front-facing camera in the Surface 2, which is designed to handle low-light settings well, which benefits Skype usage. In this case, again, Microsoft is trying to unite the physical and the digital by providing Skype premium service to people who buy Surface tablets.
